4 October 2010\n| work = TheJakartaGlobe.com\n| publisher = [[The Jakarta Globe]]\n| url = http://www.thejakartaglobe.com/home/mount-merapis-swelling-signals-huge-eruption-scientists-warn/403039\n| accessdate = 27 October 2010\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"JakartaPost2010-10-25\">\n{{cite web\n |url         = http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2010/10/25/merapi-spews-massive-lava-material.html\n |title       = Merapi spews lava\n |date        = 25 October 2010\n |work        = TheJakartaPost.com\n |publisher   = Jakarta Post\n |accessdate  = 27 October 2010\n |url-status     = dead\n |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20101028025851/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2010/10/25/merapi-spews-massive-lava-material.html\n |archivedate = 28 October 2010\n |df          = dmy-all\n}}\n</ref>\n\n}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n{{Wikinews|Merapi roars, compulsory evacuation ordered}}\n* {{wikivoyage-inline|Mount Merapi}}\n* [http://tngunungmerapi.org/ Mount Merapi National Park] \u2013 Official site {{in lang|id}}\n* [http://www.educatedearth.net/video.php?id=4290 Double Disaster in Indonesia] \u2013 Video on the 2010 eruption & tsunamis\n* [http://www.ipgp.jussieu.fr/~beaudu/merapi.html Scientific studies carried on at Merapi]\n* [http://www.lgp.cnrs.fr/spip/spip.php?article170 l\u2019Atlas du Volcan Merapi, Indon\u00e9sie/The atlas of Merapi volcano]\n\n{{Decade Volcanoes}}\n{{National parks of Indonesia}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2019}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Stratovolcanoes of Indonesia|Merapi]]\n[[Category:Subduction volcanoes|Merapi, Mount]]\n[[Category:Volcanoes of Central Java|Merapi, Mount]]\n[[Category:Mountains of Central Java|Merapi]]\n[[Category:Decade Volcanoes|Merapi, Mount]]\n[[Category:Landforms of the Special Region of Yogyakarta]]\n[[Category:Active volcanoes of Indonesia]]\n[[Category:National parks of Indonesia]]\n[[Category:VEI-4 volcanoes]]\n[[Category:21st-century volcanic events]]\n[[Category:20th-century 